Autkheṭika (HRS), officer in charge of the collection of <BR>the impost called utkheṭana (q. v.).

औत्तराह
Auttarāha (EI 8), a northerner.

औत्थितासनिक
Autthitāsanika (IE 8-3), same as Utthitāsanin; probably, <BR>courtier of a special rank provided with a special seat;<BR>perhaps, the chief nobleman at the royal court.

