avacaṭita (EI 13), a crack;<BR>cf. khaṇḍa-sphuṭit-āvacaṭita- <BR>patita-saṃskār-ārtham, ‘for the repairs of dilapidated, broken, <BR>cracked and fallen [parts]’.

