avadāna, also spelt āvadāna (EI 28, 29, 33), Oḏiyā;<BR>a <BR>present;<BR>a tax;<BR>tax in general;<BR>also called āvedana. <BR>(SITI), same as Sanskrit avasāna; termination, end.

