Avadhānin (EI 16), title of Brāhmaṇas;<BR>cf. Śatāvadhāna.

अवधारणा
avadhāraṇā, cf. adhikaraṇ-āvadhāraṇā, ‘official investiga<BR>tion’ (Ep. Ind., Vol. XXXI, p. 267).

अवधि
avadhi, cf. avadher = anantaram (LP), ‘after the time limit <BR>is over’.

अवधी
Avadhī, language of Avadh (Oudh).

