avalokya (IE 8-8), detection.

आवण
āvaṇa (SITI), Tamil;<BR>a document;<BR>generally, a sale-deed;<BR>also called vilaiy-āvaṇam; cf. āvaṇa-kkaḻari (SITI), a place <BR>where documents like sale-deeds, etc., are registered;<BR>regis<BR>tration office.

