बाहत्तरनियोगाधिपति
Bāhattaraniyogādhipati (IE 8-3;<BR>EI 23, 30), the highest <BR>executive officer under South Indian kings like the Yādavas of <BR>Devagiri;<BR>same as Bāhattaraniyogin, etc.

