jayantī-vrata (IA 6), a festival in which maṇḍapanirmāṇa- <BR>jāgaraṇa-pratimādān-ādi (erection of a shed, watching through <BR>the night, distribution of images, etc.) take place.

जयपाल
Jayapāla (SITI), a class of merchants.

जायापर
Jāyāpara (LL), probably, a householder.

जयपत्र
jaya-patra, jayarekha-patra (SITI), a certificate of victory <BR>in a dispute;<BR>a copy of the judgement. See jayarekha-patrikā. <BR>(EI 5), a certificate of success.

जयरेखपत्रिका
jayarekha-patrikā (ASLV), a certificate of victory. See <BR>jayapatra, jayarekha-patra.

