māṣaka (IE 8-8), name of a coin;<BR>cf. māṣa and dināri- <BR>māṣaka; mentioned as a silver coin (K. V. Rangaswami <BR>Aiyangar, Kṛtyakalpataru, Vyavahāra-kāṇḍa, p. 125).

