Pānīyagṛhika (LL), superintendent of a water-house. <BR>Cf. Pānīyāgārika.

पानीयक
pānīyaka (LL), a cistern.

पञ्जाबी
Pañjābī, name of the language of the Pañjāb.

पङ्क
paṅka (EI 33), a share;<BR>cf. paṅga.

पङ्क्ति
paṅkti (IE 7-1-2), ‘ten’.

