paryāya (IA 18), used in relation to an allotment. <BR>(CII 1), cf. dharma-paryāya, ‘exposition of the doctrine’;<BR>a <BR>religious text. <BR>Cf. Pallānakāra (EI 23), Sanskrit Paryāyakāra, a saddler, <BR>a saddle-maker.

