paṭṭolī, ‘a deed of purchase’ also ‘land purchased by means <BR>of a paṭṭolī’ (Jour. As. Soc., Letters, Vol. XX, p. 205). See <BR>Tamil paṭṭolai = paṭṭolā, ‘a document’.

