Pāṭy-uparika (IE 8-2;<BR>8-3;<BR>BL), official designation of <BR>uncertain implication;<BR>possibly indicating ‘the head of the de<BR>partment of accounts’;<BR>sometimes also called Mahārāja, Mahā- <BR>sāmanta, Mahāpratīhāra, Mahāpīlupati, Pañc-ādhikaraṇ-oparika <BR>and Purapāl-oparika, additionally.

