peḍā (Chamba), a grain measure;<BR>also spelt piṭha, piḍā, <BR>pyoḍā.

पेडार्पात
Peḍārpāta (BL), mistake for Peḍāpāla, ‘keeper of the record<BR>boxes’. See Peṭapāla.

पेद्दगड्यमु
