Perumān-aḍigaḻ (SITI), Tamil;<BR>a term of reverence used <BR>to indicate a god or a king. Cf. personal names like Pramāḍi.

पेरुम्बडैयोम्
perumbaḍaiyom (ASLV), military classes.

