Peṭapāla (EI 30;<BR>BL), keeper of boxes containing <BR>official records;<BR>the record-keeper.

पेटापाल
Peṭāpāla (EI 29), also called Peṭakapāla; record-keeper;<BR>same as Peṭapāla.

