pramāṇa (EI 6;<BR>SII 1;<BR>SITI), a document;<BR>a title deed. <BR>(Ep. Ind., Vol. XXVIII, p. 109), authority;<BR>witness. <BR>(SII 12), cf. mūla-pramāṇa, original order.

